data.description: Spacious 4-5 bedroom, 3 bath, 3-car garage home  situated on a 1 acre lot nestled in the quiet Oaklawn Estates subdivision.   This floor plan features a sizable living room with fireplace, a hearth room with fireplace, formal dining room, kitchen with breakfast bar, and breakfast area. The primary suite impresses with a cozy sitting area, double sinks, linen closet, two walk-in closets, a garden tub, and a separate walk-through shower with double shower heads.   This home is a must see!
